---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Nope" description="A bit about us.">
  <section class="page-shell layout-shell about-page">
    <div class="page-grid layout-grid">
      <h1 class="page-title visually-hidden">About</h1>
      <div class="about-chunk-1">
        <p>
          Nope digital is a small studio. We make websites, apps, and digital things.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-chunk-2">
        <p>
          Digital comes from <em>digitus</em>, Latin for finger. Fingers became
          digits, digits became numbers, and numbers became everything on a
          screen. Ones and zeros.
        </p>
        <p> We like that. We still make things with our fingers.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-chunk-3">
        <p>
          The name nope is intentional. We say no to most things. Not out of
          stubbornness. Out of conviction.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-chunk-4">
        <p>
          Most things don't need to exist. Extra features nobody asked for.
          Pages that fill space. Design that decorates instead of communicates.
        </p>
        <p>
          We remove all of it. What's left is usually better.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-chunk-5">
        <p>
          This is minimalism, but not as an aesthetic. As a method.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every decision starts with a question: Does this need to be here? If
          the answer isn't clearly yes, it goes.
        </p>

        <p>
          We apply this to everything: the work we take on, the words we write,
          the pixels we place.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-chunk-6">
        <p>
          We take design seriously. Not as decoration. As communication.
        </p>

        <p>
          The typeface, the spacing, the colour, the weight of a line. These
          are all decisions. Decisions made carelessly produce work that feels
          wrong even when people can't say why.
        </p>
        <p>
          We make them carefully.
        </p>

        <p>
          Good design disappears. You stop noticing it and start using it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-chunk-7">
        <p>
          The name wasn't a strategy. It was just the first honest thing.
        </p>
        <span class="signature">— Nope</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    :global([data-theme="experimental"]) .about-page {
      --color-text-primary: var(--color-text-inverse);
      --color-text-secondary: var(--color-text-inverse);
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
    }

    .page-title {
      grid-column: 1 / 4;
      font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
      font-weight: var(--font-weight-regular);
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding-top: 0.2em; /* optical alignment with body text */
    }

    .about-chunk-1,
    .about-chunk-2,
    .about-chunk-3,
    .about-chunk-4,
    .about-chunk-5,
    .about-chunk-6,
    .about-chunk-7 {
      display: grid;
      gap: var(--space-4);
      padding-block: var(--space-12);
      text-wrap: pretty;
      max-width: 32ch;
    }

    .about-chunk-1 {
      grid-column: 3 / 8;
      grid-row: 2;
    }

    .about-chunk-2 {
      grid-column: 6 / 11;
      grid-row: 3;
      margin-left: auto;
    }

    .about-chunk-3 {
      grid-column: 3 / 8;
      grid-row: 4;
    }

    .about-chunk-4 {
      grid-column: 6 / 11;
      grid-row: 5;
      margin-left: auto;
    }

    .about-chunk-5 {
      grid-column: 3 / 8;
      grid-row: 6;
    }

    .about-chunk-6 {
      grid-column: 6 / 11;
      grid-row: 7;
      margin-left: auto;
    }

    .about-chunk-7 {
      grid-column: 3 / 8;
      grid-row: 8;
    }

    .signature {
      display: block;
      margin-top: var(--space-10);
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      font-style: italic;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .about-chunk-1,
      .about-chunk-3,
      .about-chunk-5,
      .about-chunk-7 {
        grid-column: 3 / 9;
      }

      .about-chunk-2,
      .about-chunk-4,
      .about-chunk-6 {
        grid-column: 3 / 9;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .page-grid {
        row-gap: var(--space-8);
      }

      .page-title,
      .about-chunk-1,
      .about-chunk-2,
      .about-chunk-3,
      .about-chunk-4,
      .about-chunk-5,
      .about-chunk-6,
      .about-chunk-7 {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
        grid-row: auto;
        padding-block: 0;
        width: min(100%, 42rem);
        margin-inline: auto;
      }

      .about-chunk-2,
      .about-chunk-3,
      .about-chunk-4,
      .about-chunk-5,
      .about-chunk-6,
      .about-chunk-7 {
        margin-top: 0;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .signature {
        margin-top: var(--space-6);
      }

      .about-chunk-1 p,
      .about-chunk-2 p,
      .about-chunk-3 p,
      .about-chunk-4 p,
      .about-chunk-5 p,
      .about-chunk-6 p,
      .about-chunk-7 p {
        overflow-wrap: anywhere;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
